Index: linux-2.6.12-rc1/kernel/ckrm/ckrm_tc.c
===================================================================
--- /dev/null	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ linux-2.6.12-rc1/kernel/ckrm/ckrm_tc.c	2005-03-18 15:16:33.378482133 -0800
